      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this ride is. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered like a member of the family. It seriously looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! I'm only letting it go because our family is growing, but I know whoever gets behind the wheel next is going to fall in love instantly. It's a total dream to drive and truly a rare find in this kind of flawless shape. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
